{ "listsettings.baseviewmanager": [ { "_row_id": "3cd20800-4833-41fa-879b-1b2175692553", "_sequenceid": 1574, "_contextkey": null, "_contextid": null, "_createdtimestamp": "2022-07-06T08:37:37.15364", "_createddate": "2022-07-06T08:37:37.15364", "_createdsource": "Synapse Studio", "_createdchannelid": null, "_createdmessageid": null, "_createdby": "kishore rahul", "_recordstatus": 1, "_expirydate": null, "_timezonename": null, "_timezoneoffset": 0, "baseview_id": "1fb0c57a-b867-45dc-a827-9e01dc3effd8", "baseviewnamespaceid": "1ea2f183-7018-4118-aed3-d90ad6ff1548", "baseviewnamespace": "epma", "baseviewname": "encounters", "baseviewdescription": "returns all encounters for a patient", "baseviewsqlstatement": "select
CASE
	WHEN patientclasstext = 'IP' THEN 'INPATIENT ADMISSION - ' || to_char(admitdatetime AT TIME ZONE 'UTC' AT TIME ZONE 'Europe/London', 'dd/mm/yyyy') || ' (' || COALESCE(assignedpatientlocationpointofcare, 'Location not specified') || ' - ' || COALESCE(consultingdoctortext,'Consultant not specified') || ')'
	WHEN patientclasstext = 'TCI' THEN 'TCI - ' || to_char(intendedadmissiondate AT TIME ZONE 'UTC' AT TIME ZONE 'Europe/London', 'dd/mm/yyyy') || ' (' || COALESCE(specialtytext, 'Specialty not specified') || ' - ' || COALESCE(consultingdoctortext, 'Consultant not specified') || ')'

	END AS summary,
person_id,

admitdatetime, 
dischargedatetime,

patientclasscode, 
patientclasstext,

ee.specialtytext,
ce.hospitalservicetext ,
ce.hospitalservicecode,
ee.originaldateonlist, 
case when patientclasscode = 'TCI' then ee.intendedadmissiondate 
when patientclasscode = 'IP' then ce.admitdatetime 
when patientclasscode = 'W' then ee.originaldateonlist 
when patientclasscode = 'OP' then ce.admitdatetime 
end as sortdate,
COALESCE(assignedpatientlocationlocationtypetext,'') || ' (' || COALESCE(consultingdoctortext,'') || ' - ' || COALESCE(assignedpatientlocationpointofcare,'') || ')' as defaultopclinicname
FROM entitystorematerialised.core_encounter ce
LEFT JOIN entitystorematerialised.extended_encounter ee
ON ce.encounter_id = ee.encounter_id
where patientclasscode IN ('IP','TCI','W','OP')
ORDER BY 
	CASE

		WHEN patientclasstext = 'W' THEN originaldateonlist
		WHEN patientclasstext = 'OP' THEN admitdatetime
	END desc
